+# Supabase setup (Viora MVP)
+
+1) Create a Supabase project.
+2) In the SQL Editor, run the migration:
+
+- `supabase/migrations/20260302022000_viora_init.sql`
+
+3) Copy env vars into `.env.local` (and Vercel env):
+
+- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`
+- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`
+
+Docs:
+- Supabase Auth + Next.js (App Router): https://supabase.com/docs/guides/auth/quickstarts/nextjs
+- SSR client (cookies): https://supabase.com/docs/guides/auth/server-side/creating-a-client
